Description:
Gherkin/Python test cases for the Sunrise-Sunset API as described at https://sunrise-sunset.org/api


Project dependencies:
behave
requests


Installation instructions:
1) Clone repository
2) Use behave to run the sunrise_api.feature file


Additional tests that could be added:
Checking the response for latitude (+/-90) or longitude (+/-180) values that are out of range
Checking the response for latitude or longitude in an invalid format
Verifying that the times are the same in responses that are formatted and responses that aren't
